Package framework.generators

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Generator
    Abstract class to represent a wave generator.
    GeneratorPrototyper
    Provides an array of generators' prototypes.
    GuitarGenerator
    A guitar string Generator based on the Karplus-Strong algorithm.
    SawtoothGenerator
    Extends the Generator abstract class to create sawtooth waves.
    SineGenerator
    Extends the Generator abstract class to create sine waves.
    SquareGenerator
    Extends the Generator abstract class to create square waves.
    TriangleGenerator
    Extends the Generator abstract class to create triangle waves.
